[04:25.44]"Are you sure I did not throw a stone?" 
　　“你确信我一个石头也没丢吗？”

[04:28.41]"Yes. You needn't try to get out of it; I had my eye on you." 
　　“是！你不用想赖。我的眼睛一直看着你。”

